Token.Abstract: ## Version 3.2.1 - [UPDATE] Some minor refactorings - [BUGFIX] Fix NSURLSession memory leak in Swift apps - [BUGFIX] Fix issue preventing attachment from being included when sending non-clean termination report - [IMPROVEMENT] Anonymize binary path in crash report - [IMPROVEMENT] Support escaping of additional characters (URL encoding) - [IMPROVEMENT] Support Bundle Identifiers which contain whitespaces
